"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640187751,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"7c6EOGxwbgBkRJbNDcRk9-Shs7eiEb1uN4roMKu3M7k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x13de614905236c4c8B330ac38a822B25012bf398\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iMrB__qqZxXup24oMJYMvk_oYs4W4b95aKlm1mimRNI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xoy5FSUastqxqNHzw2BeREz1K4C-0UBKh_-8TfYxCiM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Med_83N-dkvRnN6FfhZZNLuN4610JEZl5BNfGUKumk5J2U22SHkmohg3RdhZqMOdhe41hFDklsgGfitDtP1q8g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9b60be86533ba0c2c758b7cf7bacc7abb06c8a2e7267be656029013faf279ab837ebb41d9c41506eea3bea50ac46cfebd8c939f2d6b5799d481e521a914d98351b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iMrB__qqZxXup24oMJYMvk_oYs4W4b95aKlm1mimRNI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xoy5FSUastqxqNHzw2BeREz1K4C-0UBKh_-8TfYxCiM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi